OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774429511
OL,3,CAdolescence leads Bafta TV nominations
OL,4,Cwith 11 nods
OL,6,FAdolescence could be set for another
OL,7,Fwinning night as the Netflix series
OL,8,Fhas received 11 nominations for the
OL,9,Fupcoming Bafta Television Awards,
OL,10,Fincluding best limited drama, leading
OL,11,Factress and leading actor.
OL,13,FStephen Graham is up for leading actor
OL,14,Ffor his role in series, while Owen
OL,15,FCooper, Ashley Walters, Christine
OL,16,FTremarco and Erin Doherty have all
OL,17,Freceived supporting actor nods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
