OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774429511
OL,3,CAdolescence leads Bafta TV nominations
OL,4,Cwith 11 nods
OL,6,FDoherty is also up for best leading
OL,7,Factress for her role A Thousand Blows,
OL,8,Fcompeting alongside actresses Aimee
OL,9,FLou Wood, Jodie Whittaker, Narges
OL,10,FRashidi, Sheridan Smith and Sian
OL,11,FBrooke.
OL,13,FAs well as Graham, Colin Firth, Matt
OL,14,FSmith, Taron Egerton, Ellis Howard and
OL,15,FJames Nelson-Joyce also received
OL,16,Fnominations for best leading actor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
