OL,3,CAdolescence leads Bafta TV nominations
OL,4,Cwith 11 nods
OL,6,FA Thousand Blows received seven
OL,7,Fnominations overall, while Andor and
OL,8,FTrespasses received six and The
OL,9,FCelebrity Traitors has five, including
OL,10,F'most memorable moment' for Alan
OL,11,FCarr's win.
