OL,3,CAdolescence leads Bafta TV nominations
OL,4,Cwith 11 nods
OL,6,FComedian Greg Davies, host of
OL,7,FTaskmaster, will present the 2026
OL,8,FBafta Television Awards, which will
OL,9,Ftake place on May 10 at the Southbank
OL,10,FCentre's Royal Festival Hall in London.
OL,12,FHere are the nominations:
OL,14,FActor in a Comedy
OL,16,FActress in a Comedy
OL,18,FDrama Series
OL,20,FEntertainment
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
